<div>
<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="5422082t" end="34200832t" region="region0" style="style0">[주제곡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="222305416t" end="233149582t" region="region0" style="style0">[가짜 예림이 흥얼거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="258591666t" end="274440832t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="457540416t" end="466716249t" region="region0" style="style0">[놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="489238749t" end="498831666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>혹시</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="505504999t" end="522605416t" region="region0" style="style0">나한테 무슨 일이 생기면...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="601434166t" end="610192916t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="616449166t" end="629795832t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>어, 어떻게 한 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="713212500t" end="723222500t" region="region0" style="style0">[거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="730312916t" end="740740000t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 침을 꿀꺽 삼킨다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle11" begin="757840416t" end="767016250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle12" begin="767850416t" end="777443332t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>뭐야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle13" begin="779945832t" end="788287500t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 놀라는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle14" begin="789121666t" end="798714582t" region="region0" style="style0">나 따라온 거?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle15" begin="802051250t" end="810392916t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle16" begin="816649166t" end="827493332t" region="region0" style="style0">어, 그런가?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle17" begin="832915416t" end="844176666t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 멋쩍은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle18" begin="845010832t" end="872121249t" region="region0" style="style0">아니, 나 그...<br/>신문부실에 가 봐야 되는데</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle19" begin="872955416t" end="881297082t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림이 살짝 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle20" begin="882131249t" end="897980416t" region="region0" style="style0">어이구, 우리 서방님</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle21" begin="907156249t" end="920502916t" region="region0" style="style0">솔직히 얘기하지 그래?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle22" begin="925090832t" end="939271666t" region="region0" style="style0">나 졸졸 따라왔잖아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle23" begin="947613332t" end="962628332t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 어색한 웃음]<br/>[가짜 예림의 옅은 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle24" begin="963462499t" end="972221249t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>아...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle25" begin="973055416t" end="1003919582t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 아니야, 나, 나 진짜<br/>신문부실에 가 봐야 돼 가지고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle26" begin="1020185832t" end="1028527499t" region="region0" style="style0">가 볼게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle27" begin="1042708332t" end="1055220832t" region="region0" style="style0">안녕, 마누라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle28" begin="1057723332t" end="1066899166t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 다급한 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle29" begin="1094426666t" end="1108607500t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle30" begin="1119451666t" end="1149898750t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예림)<br/>저 언니는<br/>진짜 예림 언니가 되고 싶어 해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle31" begin="1168250416t" end="1182431250t" region="region0" style="style0">여기서 못 나가면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle32" begin="1192024166t" end="1213295416t" region="region0" style="style0">저 언니가 진짜가 된단 말이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle33" begin="1243325416t" end="1254586666t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼 나는?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle34" begin="1285033750t" end="1299214582t" region="region0" style="style0">못 나가면 나는...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle35" begin="1328827500t" end="1340922916t" region="region0" style="style0">안 돼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle36" begin="1356772082t" end="1366365000t" region="region0" style="style0">[걱정스러운 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle37" begin="1390555832t" end="1399314582t" region="region0" style="style0">언니</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle38" begin="1464796666t" end="1475223750t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 걱정스러운 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle39" begin="1520268750t" end="1529444582t" region="region0" style="style0">[흥얼거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle40" begin="1590755832t" end="1609941666t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>이거 찾는 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle41" begin="1632464166t" end="1649147500t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle42" begin="1665830832t" end="1674172500t" region="region0" style="style0">[어이없는 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle43" begin="1690855832t" end="1699197499t" region="region0" style="style0">[떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle44" begin="1712127082t" end="1720468749t" region="region0" style="style0">상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle45" begin="1738403332t" end="1751749999t" region="region0" style="style0">그거 돌려줘</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle46" begin="1777192082t" end="1790121666t" region="region0" style="style0">돌려 달라니까!</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle47" begin="1801382916t" end="1817232082t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴박한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle48" begin="1882297082t" end="1892307082t" region="region0" style="style0">[순간 이동 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle49" begin="1921919999t" end="1931929999t" region="region0" style="style0">[순간 이동 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle50" begin="1936517916t" end="1945693749t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle51" begin="1951115832t" end="1973221249t" region="region0" style="style0">[거친 호흡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle52" begin="2005336666t" end="2030778749t" region="region0" style="style0">[힘겨운 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle53" begin="2035366666t" end="2047044999t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>서상우<br/>[긴장되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle54" begin="2090004582t" end="2099180416t" region="region0" style="style0">왜?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle55" begin="2106687916t" end="2120868749t" region="region0" style="style0">나한테 왜 이래?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle56" begin="2121702916t" end="2132547082t" region="region0" style="style0">[힘겨운 목소리로]<br/>그, 그야...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle57" begin="2141722916t" end="2157989166t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 진짜 예림이가 아니니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle58" begin="2158823332t" end="2174255416t" region="region0" style="style0">[쿵 하는 효과음]<br/>진짜, 가짜가 어디 있어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle59" begin="2179677500t" end="2199280416t" region="region0" style="style0">도대체 너 예림이를<br/>어떻게 한 거야?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle60" begin="2216797916t" end="2225556666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle61" begin="2229727500t" end="2238903332t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle62" begin="2259757500t" end="2268933332t" region="region0" style="style0">안 돼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle63" begin="2271018750t" end="2285199582t" region="region0" style="style0">얼른 다시 해 봐!</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle64" begin="2286450832t" end="2295209582t" region="region0" style="style0">안 돼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle65" begin="2298546250t" end="2317315000t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 걱정스러운 숨소리]<br/>(어린 예림)<br/>내가 안 했어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle66" begin="2331912916t" end="2350264582t" region="region0" style="style0">[다가오는 발걸음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle67" begin="2361108750t" end="2377792082t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>시간이 얼마 남지 않았구나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle68" begin="2378626250t" end="2398646250t" region="region0" style="style0">[불길한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle69" begin="2424505416t" end="2437435000t" region="region0" style="style0">(어린 예림)<br/>저 아저씨</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle70" begin="2451615832t" end="2464128332t" region="region0" style="style0">나쁜 사람</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle71" begin="2472887082t" end="2483731250t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle72" begin="2540454582t" end="2559223332t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구의 옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle73" begin="2569650416t" end="2578826250t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>자</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle74" begin="2621368750t" end="2633881250t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle75" begin="2651398750t" end="2665996666t" region="region0" style="style0">가정 교육을 잘 받았네?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle76" begin="2670584582t" end="2685599582t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게 해야 나갈 수 있어요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle77" begin="2691021666t" end="2700197500t" region="region0" style="style0">네?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle78" begin="2721468750t" end="2730644582t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨을 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle79" begin="2745242500t" end="2770267500t" region="region0" style="style0">정답은 네가 알고 있다, 강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle80" begin="2782780000t" end="2797377916t" region="region0" style="style0">아니, 모르겠어요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle81" begin="2824488332t" end="2834081250t" region="region0" style="style0">그럼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle82" begin="2848679166t" end="2859106250t" region="region0" style="style0">여기는 어디지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle83" begin="2876206666t" end="2885799582t" region="region0" style="style0">여기요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle84" begin="2907905000t" end="2917080832t" region="region0" style="style0">여기는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle85" begin="2928342082t" end="2943774166t" region="region0" style="style0">나에게는 천국이지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle86" begin="2955452500t" end="2968382082t" region="region0" style="style0">다른 누군가에게는...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle87" begin="2973387082t" end="2991738750t" region="region0" style="style0">[분위기가 고조되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle88" begin="3004251250t" end="3020100416t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>'나에게는 천국이지만'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle89" begin="3031778750t" end="3047210832t" region="region0" style="style0">'다른 누군가에게는... '</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle90" begin="3059306250t" end="3078075000t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>나 예림이야, 상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle91" begin="3078909166t" end="3089336250t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 컥컥대는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle92" begin="3090170416t" end="3100597500t" region="region0" style="style0">이거 줘</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle93" begin="3101431666t" end="3113527082t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 떨리는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle94" begin="3126456666t" end="3138969166t" region="region0" style="style0">이거</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle95" begin="3144391250t" end="3158989166t" region="region0" style="style0">던져 버릴 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle96" begin="3166913750t" end="3179426250t" region="region0" style="style0">그게 망가지면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle97" begin="3180260416t" end="3195692500t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 컥컥대는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle98" begin="3196526666t" end="3208622082t" region="region0" style="style0">사라져 버릴걸?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle99" begin="3221134582t" end="3230310416t" region="region0" style="style0">나도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle100" begin="3245742500t" end="3257420832t" region="region0" style="style0">다른 예림이도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle101" begin="3264511250t" end="3272852916t" region="region0" style="style0">[고민하는 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle102" begin="3273687082t" end="3286616666t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle103" begin="3288285000t" end="3304134166t" region="region0" style="style0">'나에게는 천국이지만'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle104" begin="3314144166t" end="3331244582t" region="region0" style="style0">'다른 누군가에게는...'</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle105" begin="3333330000t" end="3343340000t" region="region0" style="style0">[천둥이 우르릉 친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle106" begin="3344174166t" end="3357103750t" region="region0" style="style0">[슬기의 비명]<br/>[기철의 분노에 찬 비명]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle107" begin="3361274582t" end="3372535832t" region="region0" style="style0">[도희의 실성한 듯한 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle108" begin="3373369999t" end="3382545832t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle109" begin="3436349582t" end="3445525416t" region="region0" style="style0">악몽</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle110" begin="3459706249t" end="3470133332t" region="region0" style="style0">악몽이에요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle111" begin="3493489999t" end="3508922082t" region="region0" style="style0">쌤에게는 천국이지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle112" begin="3516012499t" end="3533529999t" region="region0" style="style0">우리들에게는 악몽이라고요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle113" begin="3567313749t" end="3576489582t" region="region0" style="style0">그렇다면?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle114" begin="3586082499t" end="3595675416t" region="region0" style="style0">이건</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle115" begin="3606936666t" end="3621534582t" region="region0" style="style0">단지 꿈이라고요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle116" begin="3632378749t" end="3646559582t" region="region0" style="style0">이게 내 꿈이라면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle117" begin="3657403749t" end="3673252916t" region="region0" style="style0">내 마음대로 할 수 있잖아요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle118" begin="3686599582t" end="3697860832t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle119" begin="3719132082t" end="3750413332t" region="region0" style="style0">[거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle120" begin="3752081666t" end="3765011249t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비한 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle121" begin="3847593749t" end="3861774582t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 고통스러운 신음]<br/>[털썩]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle122" begin="3883879999t" end="3893055832t" region="region0" style="style0">어, 상우야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle123" begin="3901814582t" end="3911407499t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게...</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle124" begin="3933095832t" end="3941854582t" region="region0" style="style0">[기가 찬 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle125" begin="3948527916t" end="3967713749t" region="region0" style="style0">[거친 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle126" begin="3998160832t" end="4014009999t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 거친 호흡]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle127" begin="4030693332t" end="4048627916t" region="region0" style="style0">다들 너한테 속아 왔어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle128" begin="4064059999t" end="4080326249t" region="region0" style="style0">반 아이들도, 상우도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle129" begin="4098677916t" end="4108270832t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 넌</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle130" begin="4122034582t" end="4137466666t" region="region0" style="style0">너 자신을 속였어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle131" begin="4144557082t" end="4154149999t" region="region0" style="style0">아니야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle132" begin="4176672499t" end="4190853332t" region="region0" style="style0">난 그냥 무서웠어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle133" begin="4217963749t" end="4234647082t" region="region0" style="style0">있는 그대로의 내 모습이</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle134" begin="4239652082t" end="4257169582t" region="region0" style="style0">너무 창피하고 무서웠다고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle135" begin="4299712082t" end="4312224582t" region="region0" style="style0">겁이 났어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle136" begin="4319732082t" end="4330159166t" region="region0" style="style0">미안해</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle137" begin="4335998332t" end="4344340000t" region="region0" style="style0">강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle138" begin="4357269582t" end="4373118750t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 아무런 계획도 없고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle139" begin="4379375000t" end="4399812082t" region="region0" style="style0">현재를 벗어날 용기도 없어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle140" begin="4409405000t" end="4425254166t" region="region0" style="style0">뭘 하고 싶은 건지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle141" begin="4429425000t" end="4450279166t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게 해야 행복해지는지도 몰라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle142" begin="4464042916t" end="4474052916t" region="region0" style="style0">[가짜 예림의 헛웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle143" begin="4487399582t" end="4503665832t" region="region0" style="style0">공부를 하고는 있지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle144" begin="4510756250t" end="4531193332t" region="region0" style="style0">그건 보여 주기 위한<br/>것일 뿐이라고</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle145" begin="4566645416t" end="4583328750t" region="region0" style="style0">하지만 그것도 이제는 끝이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle146" begin="4605851250t" end="4622951666t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 곧 사라지게 될 테니까</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle147" begin="4793955832t" end="4813558750t" region="region0" style="style0">[긴장감이 고조되는 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle148" begin="4821066250t" end="4830242082t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>강예림</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle149" begin="4836498332t" end="4852764582t" region="region0" style="style0">너도 나의 일부일 뿐이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle150" begin="4894890000t" end="4904900000t" region="region0" style="style0">[신비로운 효과음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle151" begin="5023768750t" end="5038783750t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>강예림<br/>[목소리가 메아리친다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle152" begin="5072567500t" end="5088833750t" region="region0" style="style0">[새들이 지저귄다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle153" begin="5101763332t" end="5115527082t" region="region0" style="style0">결론부터 말하자면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle154" begin="5150562082t" end="5160572082t" region="region0" style="style0">넌 잘했다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle155" begin="5170999166t" end="5180175000t" region="region0" style="style0">[봉구가 숨을 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle156" begin="5181009166t" end="5198943750t" region="region0" style="style0">누군가는 악몽에서 깨어나야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle157" begin="5215627082t" end="5229807916t" region="region0" style="style0">모두 돌아올 수 있지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle158" begin="5246074166t" end="5258586666t" region="region0" style="style0">강예림, 네 덕분에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle159" begin="5276104166t" end="5299460832t" region="region0" style="style0">다른 녀석들도<br/>원래대로 돌아올 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle160" begin="5309053750t" end="5318229582t" region="region0" style="style0">[헛웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle161" begin="5334078750t" end="5344505832t" region="region0" style="style0">이제부터는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle162" begin="5352847500t" end="5365777082t" region="region0" style="style0">모든 게 달라질 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle163" begin="5388299582t" end="5396641250t" region="region0" style="style0">상담은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle164" begin="5408736666t" end="5422083332t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨을 들이켠다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle165" begin="5424585832t" end="5435430000t" region="region0" style="style0">이걸로 끝이다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle166" begin="5436681250t" end="5457118332t" region="region0" style="style0">[의미심장한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle167" begin="5534695832t" end="5545540000t" region="region0" style="style0">[도희의 실성한 듯한 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle168" begin="5552213332t" end="5567228332t" region="region0" style="style0">(가짜 예림)<br/>진짜, 가짜가 어디 있어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle169" begin="5571399166t" end="5581826250t" region="region0" style="style0">[도희의 비명]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle170" begin="5887131250t" end="5896307082t" region="region0" style="style0">[똑딱]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle171" begin="5924668750t" end="5957201250t" region="region0" style="style0">[구두 발자국 소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle172" begin="5977638332t" end="5989316666t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>일어날 시간이야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle173" begin="5998492500t" end="6011005000t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>하나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle174" begin="6011839166t" end="6022266250t" region="region0" style="style0">둘</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle175" begin="6038115416t" end="6046457082t" region="region0" style="style0">셋!<br/>[카메라 셔터음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle176" begin="6047291250t" end="6060637916t" region="region0" style="style0">[짜증 섞인 신음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle177" begin="6072733332t" end="6095255832t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>아, 야, 서상우<br/>[상우의 깔깔대는 웃음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle178" begin="6099843750t" end="6109019582t" region="region0" style="style0">예림아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle179" begin="6110270832t" end="6126120000t" region="region0" style="style0">너 어제 라면 먹고 잤어?<br/>[예림의 못마땅한 숨소리]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle180" begin="6126954166t" end="6148225416t" region="region0" style="style0">얼굴 완전 빵빵해, 이거 봐 봐</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle181" begin="6149059582t" end="6158652500t" region="region0" style="style0">[깔깔대는 웃음]<br/>(예림)<br/>아, 야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle182" begin="6159486666t" end="6176170000t" region="region0" style="style0">그거 좋은 말로 할 때 안 지워?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle183" begin="6178255416t" end="6187848332t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>에헤</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle184" begin="6189516666t" end="6220797916t" region="region0" style="style0">그래도 내가 잠만 주무시는<br/>게으른 반장님 대신에</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle185" begin="6224134582t" end="6239566666t" region="region0" style="style0">전달 사항 받아 왔다고요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle186" begin="6240400832t" end="6250827916t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 잠깐만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle187" begin="6260420832t" end="6290033750t" region="region0" style="style0">오늘 조회는 없고<br/>자습이라고 했지?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle188" begin="6296290000t" end="6305465832t" region="region0" style="style0">어떻게 알았어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle189" begin="6310470832t" end="6338832500t" region="region0" style="style0">그, 담임 쌤은<br/>허리 다쳐서 입원하셨다고 했나?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle190" begin="6353430416t" end="6364274582t" region="region0" style="style0">그건 또 어떻게 알았어?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle191" begin="6378872500t" end="6392636250t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 어떻게 알았을까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle192" begin="6404731666t" end="6418495416t" region="region0" style="style0">기시감인가, 이런 게?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle193" begin="6421415000t" end="6436430000t" region="region0" style="style0">헐, 대박</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle194" begin="6448942500t" end="6457284166t" region="region0" style="style0">마누라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle195" begin="6468962500t" end="6487731250t" region="region0" style="style0">우리 점집 하나 차릴까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle196" begin="6489399582t" end="6506917082t" region="region0" style="style0">[애써 웃으며]<br/>그만해라</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle197" begin="6509002500t" end="6522349166t" region="region0" style="style0">그리고 그 카메라 내놔</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle198" begin="6523183332t" end="6544454582t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우의 장난스러운 웃음]<br/>야, 야, 카메라 내놔</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle199" begin="6545288750t" end="6554881666t" region="region0" style="style0">[잔잔한 음악]<br/>야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle200" begin="6555715832t" end="6574484582t" region="region0" style="style0">아, 야, 내 놔<br/>이것만 지워, 그러면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle201" begin="6575318750t" end="6589916666t" region="region0" style="style0">- 아, 야, 안 돼, 안 돼<br/>- 한 개만 지워</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle202" begin="6590750832t" end="6600343750t" region="region0" style="style0">- 안 돼<br/>- 아, 야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle203" begin="6633293332t" end="6649976666t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>교실에 갇힌 아이들은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle204" begin="6662906250t" end="6680423750t" region="region0" style="style0">가끔 엉뚱한 상상을 한다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle205" begin="6728388332t" end="6746739999t" region="region0" style="style0">전쟁이 일어나면 어떨까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle206" begin="6763006249t" end="6799709582t" region="region0" style="style0">지진이 나서 학교가<br/>무너져 버리는 것도 괜찮겠지</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle207" begin="6843503332t" end="6864774582t" region="region0" style="style0">나에게 세상을 바꿀 힘이 있다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle208" begin="6881040832t" end="6896055832t" region="region0" style="style0">세상은 좋아질까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle209" begin="6915658749t" end="6931507916t" region="region0" style="style0">내가 꾸는 꿈은</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle210" begin="6946522916t" end="6962372082t" region="region0" style="style0">언젠가 이루어지긴 할까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle211" begin="6991150832t" end="7013673332t" region="region0" style="style0">진심으로 간절하게 소망한다면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle212" begin="7056632916t" end="7067477082t" region="region0" style="style0">이루어질까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle213" begin="7209702499t" end="7221380832t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>뭔가</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle214" begin="7228054166t" end="7250993749t" region="region0" style="style0">긴 나쁜 꿈을 꾸고<br/>일어난 것 같아</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle215" begin="7274350416t" end="7297707082t" region="region0" style="style0">그런데 무슨 일이 있었는지는<br/>하나도 기억이 안 나</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle216" begin="7315224582t" end="7330239582t" region="region0" style="style0">원래 악몽이라는 게</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle217" begin="7338164166t" end="7369445416t" region="region0" style="style0">현실에서 생긴 나쁜 문제들을<br/>치료하는 과정이란다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle218" begin="7378204166t" end="7390716666t" region="region0" style="style0">오?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle219" begin="7392802082t" end="7407399999t" region="region0" style="style0">그러세요, 박사님?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle220" begin="7410319582t" end="7418661249t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 피식 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle221" begin="7419495416t" end="7429088332t" region="region0" style="style0">[상우가 목청을 가다듬는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle222" begin="7429922499t" end="7440766666t" region="region0" style="style0">아아, 씁</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle223" begin="7442017916t" end="7451610832t" region="region0" style="style0">그래서</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle224" begin="7456615832t" end="7471213749t" region="region0" style="style0">꿈에서 깨고 나면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle225" begin="7486228749t" end="7513756249t" region="region0" style="style0">꿈을 꾼 기억들이<br/>다 사라지는 겁니다</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle226" begin="7517092916t" end="7534610416t" region="region0" style="style0">상처가 아물듯이 말이죠</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle227" begin="7539615416t" end="7558384166t" region="region0" style="style0">[함께 웃는다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle228" begin="7567559999t" end="7575901666t" region="region0" style="style0">그래도</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle229" begin="7584660416t" end="7600926666t" region="region0" style="style0">뭔가 희미하게나마</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle230" begin="7601760832t" end="7621780832t" region="region0" style="style0">기억나는 일들이 있어</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle231" begin="7623449166t" end="7631790832t" region="region0" style="style0">그래?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle232" begin="7653062082t" end="7676418749t" region="region0" style="style0">그게 꿈인지 현실인지는</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle233" begin="7677252916t" end="7690599582t" region="region0" style="style0">잘 모르겠지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle234" begin="7703946249t" end="7714790416t" region="region0" style="style0">[예림의 후련한 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle235" begin="7735227499t" end="7754830416t" region="region0" style="style0">[함께 웃는다]<br/>[잔잔한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle236" begin="7970045416t" end="7978387082t" region="region0" style="style0">[카메라 셔터음]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle237" begin="7981723749t" end="8005080416t" region="region0" style="style0">(예림)<br/>쌤은 정말 누구세요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle238" begin="8032607916t" end="8046371666t" region="region0" style="style0">좋은 분인가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle239" begin="8048457082t" end="8060552499t" region="region0" style="style0">나쁜 분인가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle240" begin="8173999166t" end="8196104582t" region="region0" style="style0">[음산한 음악]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle241" begin="8510585416t" end="8525183332t" region="region0" style="style0">[메트로놈이 똑딱거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle242" begin="8526017499t" end="8536027499t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>자, 그럼</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle243" begin="8542700832t" end="8559801249t" region="region0" style="style0">첫 상담을 시작해 볼까?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle244" begin="8573564999t" end="8583574999t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>진짜로</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle245" begin="8588579999t" end="8604012082t" region="region0" style="style0">이걸로 찍기만 하면</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle246" begin="8607348750t" end="8624866250t" region="region0" style="style0">모든 비밀을<br/>알 수가 있는 건가요?</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle247" begin="8628202916t" end="8636544582t" region="region0" style="style0">(봉구)<br/>응</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle248" begin="8644052082t" end="8653227916t" region="region0" style="style0">하지만</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle249" begin="8660735416t" end="8674499166t" region="region0" style="style0">명심해 두는 게 좋을 거야</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle250" begin="8687845832t" end="8705363332t" region="region0" style="style0">누군가의 비밀을 엿본다는 건</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle251" begin="8714539166t" end="8735393332t" region="region0" style="style0">항상 즐겁지만은 않다는 걸</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle252" begin="8768342916t" end="8786277500t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 숨소리]<br/>[메트로놈이 똑딱거린다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle253" begin="8809634166t" end="8818392916t" region="region0" style="style0">[옅은 한숨]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle254" begin="8847588750t" end="8857598750t" region="region0" style="style0">[침을 꼴깍 삼킨다]</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle255" begin="8870111250t" end="8878870000t" region="region0" style="style0">(상우)<br/>할게요</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle256" begin="8882206666t" end="8891382500t" region="region0" style="style0">계약</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle257" begin="8900141250t" end="8909317082t" region="region0" style="style0">성립</p>
</div>
